_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;SHEET
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS *BRA* AND *BRB* ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW ARE ACTUALLY EIGHT-STRANDED BETA-BARRELS.  THESE ARE
REPRESENTED BY NINE-STRANDED SHEETS IN WHICH THE FIRST AND
LAST STRANDS ARE IDENTICAL.
;
